Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray an 8x8 pan with non-stick cooking spray. Mix crust ingredients together in a mixing bowl. Mix well. Press into prepared pan. Bake 10-12 minutes or until firm. Mix cream cheese and SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener together until smooth. Add eggs, one at a time, scraping the sides of the bowl, and mixing well after each addition. Add sour cream and extracts; mix well. Pour over prepared crust. Bake in preheated oven for 40 to 47 minutes, or until firm. Top with toasted almonds.